title: Selling the OC Recap with Megan Gailey
itunes:title: Selling the OC Recap with Megan Gailey
description:
Danny is joined by comedian/host Megan Gailey to recap season 1 of Selling the OC, an important Netflix series about OC realtors. Danny and Megan discuss the true villains, Tyler's relationship with Brittany Snow, drama with Gio's wife, his mother, and so much more!
